Consciously crafted using recycled plastic bottles,Extreme breathability with Coolmax(r) Fiber,High-IQ(r) no-fade eco-friendly colours,Premium moisture wicking pique fabric,Tested to retain shape and colour for 500 Days 1. Earth's most loved: Where the world sees trash, we saw a chance to turn trash into fashion. This Shirt for Men, has recycled polyester made from plastic bottles disposed in the oceans. Add to that, a sustainably sourced ethical cotton, makes this Shirt, your most earth friendly one yet.
2. The coolest ever: A Shirt so cool on you and nature. Featuring the globally acclaimed Coolmax(r) Fiber, Constant Pique Shirts are so breathable and airy, it's never going to get hot in here. It's designed to thermoregulate the body temperature so you feel good all year long.
3. Conscious colours: Only the most eco-friendly dyes have been used to colour up these Shirts. The HIGH-IQ(r) Colour Retention programme makes the longest lasting, maximum water and energy saving dyes in the industry. You'll see the difference.
